data.description: Historic Brick duplex across from Dailey park in Baker boasts 1 bed, 1 bath with living room, dining room and kitchen with full basements to include a garage on each side! The beautiful hardwood floors and tall ceilings are just a few of the highlights to include big bountiful backyards, perfect for croquet. The units have been remodeled and would be perfect for an owner to buy and live in one side and rent the other or do Airbnb. If all this wasn’t enough, the seller has an FHA mortgage of 2.49% that is assumable, the current mortgage to assume is $592,196 for those who qualify! No HOA, perfectly maintained, this is your chance to grab two properties for the price of one with an historically low interest rate.
